wharepuni
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Maori sleeping house
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: whare-puni, whare puni Thick walled house built for warmth, as for sleeping quarters but includes general 'warm house' use.
